headline: How Will Dow Jones Futures React To Trump-EU Trade Deal? Tesla 'Robotaxis,' Earnings Wave In Focus
summary: A U.S-EU trade deal avoids a Trump tariff hike. Meta, Amazon lead an earnings wave. Tesla "robotaxis" will come to San Francisco.
